  <brief_title>Simvastatin Therapy in Women With Polycystic Ovary Syndrome.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Simvastatin on Clinical, Endocrine, Metabolic and Biochemical Parameters of Women With Polycystic Ovary Syndrome: Prospective, Randomized Trial.</official_title>
