  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether statins (simvastatin) improve clinical
      (excessive hair, skin problems), endocrine (androgens) and metabolic (lipids, markers of
      systemic inflammation) in women with polycystic ovary syndrome (PCOS).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
